title: "Unsupported floating point instruction" on arm5 - sheevaplug
body:
by **fgergo**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. "make -C math test" fails during all.bash

What is the expected output?
Test should PASS, as all tests before it.

What do you see instead?
see end of page:
http://gosheeva.blogspot.com/2011/03/2011-03-232100281ca16d1788batxt.html

Which compiler are you using (5g, 6g, 8g, gccgo)?
5g
# set|grep GO
GOARCH=arm
GOARM=5
GOOS=linux
GOROOT=/n/sd/1/go

Which operating system are you using?
# uname -a
Linux dugo 2.6.22.18 #1 Thu Mar 19 14:46:22 IST 2009 armv5tejl GNU/Linux

Which revision are you using?  (hg identify)
# hg identify
c5c62aeb6267+ release.r56/weekly.2011-03-07.1/release

Please provide any additional information below.
